  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience a taste of the charming 2D platformer that will test your speed and skill!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What's Included in the game:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >32 unique levels showcasing the game's pixel art graphics and clever design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 playable characters with distinct abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local time trial high score table</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race through beautifully crafted 2D environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect the most cherries while aiming for the fastest completion time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover multiple paths to the finish line</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the core gameplay mechanics that make Cherry Jump unique</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet the Cherry Jumpers!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/c2fdeccf7586cbbdcbe9ce7969a3146f.webp?t=1732686728\" width=32 height=32 /></span><strong>Cherry Blossom</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cherry Blossom is our classic protagonist! With balanced speed and agility, perfect for newcomers and seasoned players alike. Master the basics and discover the joy of cherry jumping with this well-rounded character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/b3a5859b5feab1eabfc269c4e7650b31.poster.avif?t=1732686728\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/b3a5859b5feab1eabfc269c4e7650b31.webm?t=1732686728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/b3a5859b5feab1eabfc269c4e7650b31.mp4?t=1732686728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hop-Along</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/40508cae47002a6941081a5be187b1f4.webp?t=1732686728\" width=32 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hop-Along is the wall-climbing wonder! This green dynamo can stick to walls, opening up new pathways and strategies. Use his unique ability to navigate tricky vertical challenges and find hidden shortcuts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/7991082a4bb7d8ec78fceac67fa4c2aa.poster.avif?t=1732686728\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/7991082a4bb7d8ec78fceac67fa4c2aa.webm?t=1732686728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/7991082a4bb7d8ec78fceac67fa4c2aa.mp4?t=1732686728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/ee349d44a7620faaff1b4d94d8c28518.webp?t=1732686728\" width=32 height=32 /></span><strong>Blink</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blink is the master of shortcuts! With his teleportation ability, he can zip through short distances, phasing through obstacles. Perfect for speedrunners looking to shave seconds off their best times!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/e779afd2a81c6a7ff357db4607842499.poster.avif?t=1732686728\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/e779afd2a81c6a7ff357db4607842499.webm?t=1732686728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/e779afd2a81c6a7ff357db4607842499.mp4?t=1732686728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Candlewick</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/56daae2d27acaf26dac392fff77b4eca.webp?t=1732686728\" width=32 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Candlewick brings the heat to Cherry Jump! This fiery character can rejump off candles, turning obstacles into launch pads. Use this unique ability to reach new heights and discover secret areas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/20e10711076ffa74588a753978278ffc.poster.avif?t=1732686728\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/20e10711076ffa74588a753978278ffc.webm?t=1732686728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/20e10711076ffa74588a753978278ffc.mp4?t=1732686728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Cherry Jump Demo gives you a glimpse into the fast-paced world of the full game. Perfect your runs, explore the levels, and get a feel for the delightful gameplay that awaits in the complete version.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience a taste of the charming 2D platformer that will test your speed and skill!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What's Included in the game:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >32 unique levels showcasing the game's pixel art graphics and clever design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 playable characters with distinct abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local time trial high score table</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race through beautifully crafted 2D environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect the most cherries while aiming for the fastest completion time</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover multiple paths to the finish line</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the core gameplay mechanics that make Cherry Jump unique</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet the Cherry Jumpers!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/c2fdeccf7586cbbdcbe9ce7969a3146f.webp?t=1732686728\" width=32 height=32 /></span><strong>Cherry Blossom</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cherry Blossom is our classic protagonist! With balanced speed and agility, perfect for newcomers and seasoned players alike. Master the basics and discover the joy of cherry jumping with this well-rounded character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/b3a5859b5feab1eabfc269c4e7650b31.poster.avif?t=1732686728\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai