unners looking to shave seconds off their best times!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/e779afd2a81c6a7ff357db4607842499.poster.avif?t=1732686728\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/e779afd2a81c6a7ff357db4607842499.webm?t=1732686728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/e779afd2a81c6a7ff357db4607842499.mp4?t=1732686728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Candlewick</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/56daae2d27acaf26dac392fff77b4eca.webp?t=1732686728\" width=32 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Candlewick brings the heat to Cherry Jump! This fiery character can rejump off candles, turning obstacles into launch pads. Use this unique ability to reach new heights and discover secret areas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/20e10711076ffa74588a753978278ffc.poster.avif?t=1732686728\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/20e10711076ffa74588a753978278ffc.webm?t=1732686728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3182400/extras/20e10711076ffa74588a753978278ffc.mp4?t=1732686728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Cherry Jump Demo gives you a glimpse into the fast-paced world of the full game. Perfect your runs, explore the levels, and get a feel for the delightful gameplay that awaits in the complete version.</p>",
